OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will start dry with some
OL,6,Fearly brightness across the south and
OL,7,Feast, otherwise cloudy with outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain, heaviest and most persistent
OL,9,Facross western parts.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will remain cloudy during
OL,12,Fthe evening and through the night with
OL,13,Foutbreaks of rain, turning heavy and
OL,14,Fperhaps thundery from late evening.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FCloud and occasionally heavy,
OL,17,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing.
OL,18,FThen sunny spells and scattered
OL,19,Fshowers, occasionally heavy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
